HOST: http://developer.marveldbs.me/api

# MarvelDB

MarvelDB is an API allowing users to retrieve information about their
favorite characters, comics, creators, and series of the vast Marvel
universe.

More REST endpoints to come.

## Characters [/characters]

### List All Characters [GET]

Returns a list of all the characters in the MarvelDBS database.
Characters appear in comics and series but are not associated with
creators.

Filtering to come in the future.

