## Creators [/creators]

### List All Creators [GET]

Returns a list of all the creators in the MarvelDBS database.
Creators are credited with their respective comics and series but not
with characters.

Filtering to come in the future.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 30,
                "fullName": "Stan Lee",
                "thumbnail": "http://i.annihil.us/u/prod/marvel/i/mg/9/d0/4bc37d9d8f541.jpg",
